version_description: Chords Have been taken from the tab and simplified for acoustic guitar.
Chord positions at bottom of tab.
Synth part at the start now added.

Studio version from "Metropolis pt.2" album. The main piano arpeggio consistently hits F#, thus the alterations in many chords (9ths #11ths, etc.). May work decently with basic triads, too. Wrote this to have a quick chords reference for guitar and piano.

version_description: All parts of the song included, with chords derived from synth and guitar/bass parts.
This version shows what chords would be played over the tapping section of Eruption.
